.DS_Store
scratch/.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# ── Orphan / auto-generated files ──
Docs/Milestones/Untitled
Docs/Research/Untitled
Docs/plan_review.md.resolved

# ── IDE / editor config (personal preferences) ──
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
